0good%20option%20while%20we%20wait%20for%20mortgage%20rates%20to%20ease.%20Check%20out%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-heloc-lenders%5C%22%3Ebest%20HELOC%20lenders%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20start%20your%20search%20for%20the%20right%20loan%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20HELOC%20is%20a%20line%20of%20credit%20that%20lets%20you%20borrow%20against%20the%20equity%20in%20your%20home.%20It%20works%20similarly%20to%20a%20credit%20card%20in%20that%20you%20borrow%20what%20you%20need%20rather%20than%20getting%20the%20full%20amount%20you're%20borrowing%20in%20a%20lump%20sum.%20It%20also%20lets%20you%20tap%20into%20the%20money%20you%20have%20in%20your%20home%20without%20replacing%20your%20entire%20mortgage%2C%20like%20you'd%20do%20with%20a%20cash-out%20refinance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22e3f3577dfe678e19f8dce895f3061b13%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcurrent-heloc-rates%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22e3f3577dfe678e19f8dce895f3061b13%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcurrent-heloc-rates%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%3ECurrent%20HELOC%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0are%20relatively%20low%20compared%20to%20other%20loan%20options%2C%20including%20credit%20cards%20and%20personal%20loans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhen%20Will%20House%20Prices%20Come%20Down%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20aren't%20likely%20to%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhome-prices-drop%5C%22%3Ehome%20prices%20drop%3C%2Fa%3E%20anytime%20soon%20thanks%20to%20extremely%20limited%20supply.%20In%20fact%2C%20they'll%20likely%20rise%20this%20year%20as%20mortgage%20rates%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanniemae.com%2Fmedia%2F50801%2Fdisplay%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFannie%20Mae%20researchers%3C%2Fa%3E%20expect%20prices%20to%20increase%203.2%25%20in%202024%2C%20while%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mba.org%2Fnews-and-research%2Fforecasts-and-commentary%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMortgage%20Bankers%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20expects%20a%204.1%25%20increase%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELower%20mortgage%20rates%20will%20bring%20more%20buyers%20onto%20the%20market%2C%20putting%20upward%20pressure%20on%20prices.%20But%20prices%20aren't%20currently%20expected%20to%20increase%20as%20much%20as%20they%20have%20in%20recent%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFixed-Rate%20vs.%20Adjustable-Rate%20Mortgage%20Pros%20and%20Cons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-fixed-rate-mortgage%5C%22%3EFixed-rate%20mortgages%3C%2Fa%3E%20lock%20in%20your%20rate%20for%20the%20entire%20life%20of%20your%20loan.%20Adjustable-rate%20mortgages%20lock%20in%20your%20rate%20for%20the%20first%20few%20years%2C%20then%20your%20rate%20goes%20up%20or%20down%20periodically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20do%20you%20choose%20between%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ffixed-rate-mortgage-vs-adjustable-rate-mortgage%5C%22%3Efixed-rate%20vs.%20adjustable-rate%20mortgage%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EARMs%20typically%20start%20with%20lower%20rates%20than%20fixed-rate%20mortgages%2C%20but%20ARM%20rates%20can%20go%20up%20once%20your%20initial%20introductory%20period%20is%20over.%20If%20you%20plan%20on%20moving%20or%20refinancing%20before%20the%20rate%20adjusts%2C%20an%20ARM%20could%20be%20a%20good%20deal.%20But%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20a%20change%20in%20circumstances%20could%20prevent%20you%20from%20doing%20these%20things%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20think%20about%20whether%20your%20budget%20could%20handle%20a%20higher%20monthly%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFixed-rate%20mortgage%20are%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20borrowers%20who%20want%20stability%2C%20since%20your%20monthly%20principal%20and%20interest%20payments%20won't%20change%20throughout%20the%20life%20of%20the%20loan%20(though%20your%20mortgage%20payment%20could%20increase%20if%20your%20taxes%20or%20insurance%20go%20up).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20exchange%20for%20this%20stability%2C%20you'll%20take%20on%20a%20higher%20rate.%20This%20might%20seem%20like%20a%20bad%20deal%20right%20now%2C%20but%20if%20rates%20increase%20further%20down%20the%20road%2C%20you%20might%20be%20glad%20to%20have%20a%20rate%20locked%20in.%20And%20if%20rates%20trend%20down%2C%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20refinance%20to%20snag%20a%20lower%20rate%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20Does%20an%20Adjustable-Rate%20Mortgage%20Work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fadjustable-rate-mortgage%5C%22%3EAdjustable-rate%20mortgages%3C%2Fa%3E%20start%20with%20an%20introductory%20period%20where%20your%20rate%20will%20remain%20fixed%20for%20a%20certain%20period%20of%20time.%20Once%20that%20period%20is%20up%2C%20it%20will%20begin%20to%20adjust%20periodically%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20once%20per%20year%20or%20once%20every%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20your%20rate%20will%20change%20depends%20on%20the%20index%20that%20the%20ARM%20uses%20and%20the%20margin%20set%20by%20the%20lender.%20Lenders%20choose%20the%20index%20that%20their%20ARMs%20use%2C%20and%20this%20rate%20can%20trend%20up%20or%20down%20depending%20on%20current%20market%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20margin%20is%20the%20amount%20of%20interest%20a%20lender%20charges%20on%20top%20of%20the%20index.%20You%20should%20shop%20around%20with%20multiple%20lenders%20to%20see%20which%20one%20offers%20the%20lowest%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EARMs%20also%20come%20with%20limits%20on%20how%20much%20they%20can%20change%20and%20how%20high%20they%20can%20go.%20For%20example%2C%20an%20ARM%20might%20be%20limited%20to%20a%202%25%20increase%20or%20decrease%20every%20time%20it%20adjusts%2C%20with%20a%20maximum%20rate%20of%208%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-mortgage-refinance-rates-today-saturday-6-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712397601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F626bf7be86fa90001905c9f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-mortgage-refinance-rates-today-saturday-6-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20are%20today's%20mortgage%20and%20refinance%20rates.%20Mortgage%20rates%20spiked%20above%206.5%25%20this%20week%2C%20but%20they%20should%20start%20to%20trend%20back%20down%20as%20inflation%20slows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Molly%20Grace)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-mortgage-refinance-rates-today-saturday-6-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gen%20Zers%2C%20take%20note%3A%20Some%20boomers%20have%20found%20a%20simple%20path%20to%20happiness%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Back%20of%20older%20couple%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660ea99e3f923f7dab048260%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221415%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAscent%20Xmedia%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20World%20Happiness%20Report%20found%20happiness%20among%20young%20people%20in%20North%20America%20declined.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOlder%20adults%20in%20the%20US%20had%20higher%20happiness%20levels%2C%20even%20though%20they%20had%20fewer%20social%20interactions.%3C%2Fli