piness%20is%20high%20for%20young%20people%2C%20it%20bottoms%20out%20in%20middle%20age%2C%20and%20it%20increases%20again%20at%20old%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-solve-loneliness-older-adult-planning-retirement-biggest-fear-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloneliness%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20younger%20generations%20were%20hit%20the%20hardest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLoneliness%20is%20almost%20twice%20as%20high%20among%20the%20Millennials%20than%20among%20those%20born%20before%201965%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%20%26quot%3BMillennials%20also%20feel%20less%20socially%20supported%20than%20Boomers%20in%20those%20countries%2C%20another%20place%20in%20which%20these%20countries%20look%20different%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20This%20is%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20actual%20social%20connections%20are%20much%20more%20frequent%20for%20Millennials%20than%20Boomers%2C%20and%20about%20as%20frequent%20as%20for%20Generation%20X.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bthose%20in%20the%20boomer%20and%20earlier%20generations%20feel%20more%20socially%20supported%20and%20less%20lonely%20than%20those%20in%20the%20younger%20generations%20despite%20having%20less%20frequent%20actual%20interactions%20with%20all%20groups%20except%20neighbours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20range%20of%20possibilities%20could%20explain%20why%20this%20might%20be%20the%20case.%20Preeti%20Malani%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20medicine%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bloneliness%20is%20far%2C%20far%20greater%20among%20the%20younger%20group.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20lonely%20as%20an%2080-year-old%20may%20be%20due%20to%20a%20very%20different%20reason%20than%20someone%20who%20is%20a%2019-year-old%20college%20student%20living%20amongst%20a%20huge%20group%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Malani%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20be%20surrounded%20by%20people%20and%20be%20lonely.%20And%20that%20college%20experience%20or%20high%20school%20experience%20is%20a%20good%20example%20where%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20meaningful%20connections%20with%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20on%20meaningful%20connections%20might%20just%20be%20what%20splits%20older%20generations%20from%20younger%20generations%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20happiness.%20While%20some%20Gen%20Zers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-loneliness-spends-money-to-make-friends-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20spent%20money%20to%20make%20more%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20social%20clubs%20and%20fitness%20groups%2C%20older%20adults%20have%20told%20BI%20that%20for%20them%2C%20it's%20not%20about%20the%20quantity%20of%20their%20social%20connections%3B%20it's%20about%20the%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESusan%20Skinner%2C%20a%2071-year-old%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpreventing-loneliness-solutions-boomers-taco-tuesdays-phone-contacts-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20took%20her%20a%20while%20to%20establish%20close%20friendships%2C%20but%20for%20her%20well-being%20and%20happiness%2C%20the%20effort%20is%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20remember%20the%20research%20on%20how%20many%20hours%20together%20it%20takes%20to%20make%20someone%20a%20close%20friend%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20having%20someone%20where%20you%20could%20think%2C%20'Would%20this%20be%20someone%20I%20could%20call%20up%20and%20say%20that%20I'm%20just%20having%20a%20really%20bad%20day%2C%20I%20need%20to%20talk%2C%20or%20just%20tell%20me%20what's%20going%20on%20with%20you%2C'%20something%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERoadblocks%20to%20happiness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%