202022%20and%20testing%20a%20previous%20model%20at%20an%20H%26amp%3BM%20Williamsburg%20pop-up%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhm-sustainability-goals-building-tiles-biomason-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EH%26amp%3BM%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20experimented%20with%20other%20tech%2C%20like%20voice%20interactive%20mirrors%20at%20its%20flagship%20store%20in%20Times%20Square.%20The%20mirror%20was%20activated%20through%20facial%20recognition%20and%20offered%20selfies%2C%20style%20advice%2C%20and%20discounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdesigner-creates-smart-mirror-like-giant-apple-iphone-2016-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESoho%20smart%20mirrors%20aren't%20the%20first%20of%20their%20kind%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20technology%20hasn't%20quite%20made%20it%20to%20mainstream%20retail%20stores%20yet.%20Other%20brands%20have%20tried%20out%20similar%20technology%2C%20though%2C%20including%20Ralph%20Lauren%2C%20Neiman%20Marcus%2C%20Superdry%2C%20and%20Speedo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mirrors%20are%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20attempt%20to%20implement%20tech-enabled%20in-store%20shopping%20solutions%2C%20according%20to%20an%20H%26amp%3BM%20press%20release%20announcing%20the%20launch%20in%202022.%20Other%20changes%20include%20seamless%20payment%20methods%20and%20upgraded%20delivery%20and%20return%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20went%20to%20the%20new%20store%20location%20in%20Soho%20to%20check%20out%20the%20mirrors.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22H%26amp%3BM%20soho%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661010f216bde8d4ead60932%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EH%26amp%3BM's%20new%20Soho%20location%20opened%20in%20February.%20%3Cp%3EAna%20Altchek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2010%2C000-square-foot%20store%20is%20located%20on%20591%20Broadway%20and%20every%20fitting%20room%20has%20a%20smart%20mirror.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20H%26amp%3BM%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20store%20is%20collecting%20qualitative%20feedback%20on%20the%20mirrors%20directly%20from%20customers%20and%20store%20employees.%20It%20has%20also%20sent%20surveys%20to%20customers%20within%20its%20loyalty%20program.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20smart%20mirrors%20are%20located%20in%20the%20dressing%20rooms.%20They%20have%20an%20H%26amp%3BM%20logo%20in%20red%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20screen%2C%20and%20you%20may%20have%20to%20turn%20them%20on%20by%20selecting%20'show%20screen.'%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222594%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22H%26amp%3BM%20mirror%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6610297c16bde8d4ead619e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223458%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20smart%20mirrors%20look%20just%20like%20regular%20mirrors%20but%20have%20a%20logo%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bshow%20screen%26quot%3B%20button.%20%3Cp%3EAna%20Altchek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20not%20notice%20the%20mirror%20when%20you%20walk%20in%20because%20it%20looks%20just%20like%20a%20regular%20mirror%20and%20it%20may%20be%20%26quot%3Basleep%26quot%3B%20when%20you%20enter%2C%20just%20like%20your%20phone%20or%20laptop%20if%20it%20hasn't%20been%20used.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20smart%20mirrors%20have%20a%20logo%20in%20the%20right%20corner%20though%20and%20you%20can%20turn%20them%20on%20by%20selecting%20%26quot%3Bshow%20screen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20mirror%20automatically%20scans%20the%20items%20and%20displays%20them%20on%20the%20mirror%20so%20you%20can%20view%20the%20details%20and%20check%20out%20different%20colors%20and%20sizes.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221060%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%225%20items%20on%20H%26amp%3BM%20smart%20mirror%20display%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6610291e3f923f7dab051014%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221234%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20see%20the%20item's%20description%2C%20all%20the%20sizes%20and%20colors%20available%2C%20and%20options%20to%20style%20it%20with.%3Cp%3EAna%20Altchek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20that%20if%20you%20immediately%20hang%20the%20items%2C%20the%20smart%20mirror%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20accurately%20scan%20them%20so%20you%20have%20to%20wait%20a%20few%20seconds%20before%20setting%20the%20clothes%20down.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20it%20shows%20the%20correct%20items%2C%20you%20can%20scroll%20through%20and%20select%20different%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20screen%20will%20show%20you%20a%20description%20of%20the%20item%2C%20as%20well%20as%20different%20sizes%20and%20colors%20available.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20try%20a%20different%20color%20or%20size%2C%20you%20can%20request%20it%20on%20the%20mirror%20without%20having%20to%20call%20over%20staff%20outside%20the%20room.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22940%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Size%20request%20H%26amp%3BM%20smart%20mirror%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661045801caec1275a6d6024%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22608%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20try%20a%20different%20dize%20or%20color%2C%20you%20can%20request%20it%20on%20the%20smart%20mirror.%20%3Cp%3EAna%20Altchek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20select%20a%20size%20or%20color%2C%20the%20screen%20will%20ask%20if%20you%20want%20to%20request%20it.%20It%20will%20also%20tell%20you%20if%20the%20size%20or%20color%20you%20want%20isn't%20available%2C%20and%20you%20can%20order%20it%20online%20on%20the%20spot%20by%20scanning%20a%20QR%20code.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20will%20show%20up%20as%20a%20request%20while%20it's%20on%20its%20way%20to%20your%20room.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22requ