ns%20Sparkd%2C%20one%20of%20the%20only%20mind-body%20fitness%20gyms%20in%20the%20world%2C%20has%20just%20invited%20me%20in%20for%20a%20tour%20of%20her%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20exercise%20space%20is%20a%20funhouse%20for%20grown-ups%2C%20located%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20downtown%20Singapore's%20financial%20district%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgfmag.com%2Fbanking%2Fsingapore-asian-banking-magnet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAsian%20banking%20capital%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20treadmill%20ramps%20up%20and%20down%20in%20all%20four%20directions%2C%20the%20barbells%20have%20slime-like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-tonal-high-tech-home-gym-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edynamic%20weights%3C%2Fa%3E%20sloshing%20around%20inside%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20virtual%20soccer%20simulator%20wall.%20It's%20hard%20for%20clients%20to%20get%20bored%20here%2C%20she%20tells%20me%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sparkd%20gym%20in%20Singapore%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66106ec71caec1275a6d7eee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221182%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESparkd%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20mind-blowing%20toy%20in%20the%20space%20is%20sitting%20in%20the%20corner.%20It's%20the%20NeuroTracker%2C%20a%20brain%20game%20developed%20more%20than%2014%20years%20ago%20by%20a%20Canadian%20visual%20perception%20scientist%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20still%20a%20somewhat%20controversial%20device.%20Independent%20experts%20in%20sports%20science%20say%20it%20seems%20like%20it%20has%20decent%20potential%20for%20improving%20our%20attention%2C%20memory%2C%20and%20processing%20speeds%2C%20but%20more%20rigorous%20independent%20research%20is%20needed%20to%20understand%20to%20what%20extent%20it's%20a%20placebo%20effect.%20And%20yet%2C%20franchises%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.neurotrackerx.com%2Fpost%2F7-pro-athletes-give-2-cents-neurotracker%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-profile%20athletes%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20world%20are%20snapping%20it%20up.%20The%20US%20Air%20Force%2C%20Manchester%20United%2C%20and%20the%20Atlanta%20Falcons%20have%20all%20used%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESingapore%20is%20modeling%20the%20brain-body%20workout%20of%20the%20future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22885%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20standing%20using%20neurotracker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6610704f3f923f7dab054318%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22590%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENeuroTracker%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20the%20NeuroTracker%20looks%20like%20a%20slightly%20boring%20video%20game%20you%20play%20while%20wearing%203D%20glasses.%20Just%20some%20neon%20green%20balls%20moving%20around%20on%20a%20computer%20screen.%20After%20one%20session%2C%20roughly%20six%20minutes%20of%20wearing%20blue%20and%20red%20glasses%20and%20staring%20at%20the%20screen%2C%20I%20(a%20skeptical%20reporter)%20am%20surprised%20by%20how%20I'm%20feeling.%20I%20think%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20get%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStay%20focused%2C%26quot%3B%20Milani%20says%2C%20encouraging%20me%20along%20with%20the%20NeuroTracker.%20It%20feels%20surprisingly%20energizing%20to%20give%20this%20kind%20of%20singular%20attention%20to%20the%20task%20of%20watching%20balls%20on%20a%20screen.%20This%20is%20ostensibly%20training%20my%20brain%20to%20focus%2C%20and%20improving%20my%20working%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hilary%20at%20sparkd%2C%20planking%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6610707f16bde8d4ead64e88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnna%20Milani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20neuro-tracking%20is%20just%20one%20fundamental%20part%20of%20Milani's%20gym.%20Here%2C%20exercisers%20are%20always%20working%20on%20both%20their%20physical%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20mental%20agility.%20I'm%20not%20doing%20my%20planks%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20I'm%20doing%20them%20(or%2C%20attempting%20to%2C%20anyway)%20on%20a%20moving%20platform%20that%20challenges%20my%20balance.%20Instead%20of%20staring%20at%20a%20wall%20while%20I%20do%20squats%20with%20a%20medicine%20ball%2C%20Milani%20has%20me%20doing%20a%20memory%20game%20with%20letters%20and%20numbers.%20This%20is%20not%20zone-out-and-clear-your-mind%20cardio.%20This%20is%20total%20performance%20enhancement.%20And%20emerging%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.verifiedmarketreports.com%2Fproduct%2Fbrain-fitness-market%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20business%20interest%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20gyms%20around%20the%20globe%20is%20starting%20to%20crop%20up%20around%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20age%2C%20and%20proprioception%20(our%20awareness%20of%20our%20own%20body%20in%20space)%20declines%2C%20it%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F68-year-old-athlete-shares-workouts-to-live-to-100-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egets%20harder%20to%20perform%20physical%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20mental%20tasks%20in%20tandem.%20Even%20walking%20and%20talking.%20Milani%2C%20a%20former%20dancer%2C%20says%20she%20started%20noticing%20subtle%20changes%20in%20herself%20once%20she%20hit%20her%2040s%3B%20that's%20what%20prompted%20her%20to%20found%20this%20space%20about%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hilary%20at%20sparkd%20playing%20mind%20games%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661070eb3f923f7dab05433a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20work%20out%20your%20body%20and%20your%20brain%20at%20the%20same%20time!%3Cp%3EAnna%20Milani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20first-of-its-kind%20brain%20gym%20is%20already%20popular%20with%20many%20of%20Singapore's%20longevity-focused%20business%20executives.%20The%20same%20guys%20who%20spend%20their%20days%20buying%20and%20selling%20companies%20and%20their%20spare%20time%20tracking%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-experts-keep-biological-age-young-anti-aging-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiological%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20here%20regularly%2C%20Milani%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENothing%20like%20it%20really%20exists%20yet%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20unless%20you're%20a%20pro%20athlete.%20Pro%20athletes%20in%20the%20NFL%2C%20NBA%2C%20NHL%2C%20and%20MLB%20have%20incorporated%20Neurotracker%20into%20their%20training%20to%20level%20up.%20One%20college%20athlete%20credits%20the%20technology%20with%20helping%20her%20win%20a%20gold%20medal%20at%20the%20Winter%20Olympics.%20Online%20stock%20traders%20(29%20of%20them%2C%20all%20men)%20also%20recently%20used%20it%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.neurotrackerx.com%2Fpost%2Fnew-research-neurotracker-predicts-the-profitability-of-traders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egauge%20whether%20they%20were%20having%20an%20off%20day%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20their%20scores%20from%20six-minute%20tracking%20sessions%20dipped%20well%20below%20their%20own%20baseline%2C%20they%20could%20take%20the%20day%20off%2C%20knowing%20their%20performance%20wasn't%20likely%20to%20be%20up%20to%20par.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrain%20training%20for%20longevity%20is%20still%20squishy%20science%2C%20for%20now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20training%20could%20soon%20be%20rolled%20out%20wider%2C%20buoyed%20by%20some%20research%20that%20suggests%20benefits.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.neurotrackerx.com%2Fpost%2Fnew-research-perceptual-cognitive-training-improves-motor-skills-in-aging%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20Neurotracker%20conducted%20at%20a%20major%20hospital%20in%20Mexico%20City%2C%20older%20adults%20with%20mild%20dementia%20and%20memory%20issues%20had%20better%20fine%20motor%20control%20and%20hand-eye%20coordination%20after%20about%2090%20minutes%20of%20the%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20Sidebottom%2C%20NeuroTracker's%20director%20of%20concept%20applications%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20company%20is%20in%20a%20late-stage%20partnership%20deal%20with%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20major%20fitness%20chains%20in%20the%20US%26quot%3B%20(though%20the%20company%20wouldn't%20say%20which%20one).%20Gyms%20and%20clubs%20leaning%20harder%20into%20the%20longevity%20space%20are%20looking%20at%20Milani%20as%20an%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20all%20kind%20of%20discussing%20it%2C%20and%20feel%20like%20they%20have%20a%20need%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20cognitive%20dimension%20to%20the%20physical%20fitness%2C%26quot%3B%20Sidebottom%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20see%20increases%20in%20physical%20reaction%20time%2C%20we%20see%20improvements%20in%20auditory%20processes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20independent%20sports%20scientists%20aren't%20totally%20sure%20about%20that.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC8500884%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2021%20systematic%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Neurotracker%20studies%20found%20that%20the%20company%20tends%20to%20overstate%20its%20data%2C%20and%20that%20more%20people%20need%20to%20test%20out%20this%20tech%20to%20know%20for%20sure%20that%20the%20results%20aren't%20just%20indicative%20of%20false%20positives%20and%20a%20placebo%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20step%20out%20onto%20the%20sparkling-clean%20Singaporean%20pavement%2C%20jumping%20to%20dart%20around%20mid-afternoon%20rain%20puddles%20in%20the%20tropical%20heat%2C%20I%20feel%20refreshed%20and%20sharp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20impossible%20for%20me%20to%20disentangle%20exactly%20how%20much%20of%20that%20feeling%20could%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20physical%20workout%20I%20just%20did%2C%20how%20much%20of%20it%20was%20the%20mental%20exercises%2C%20and%20how%20much%20may%20be%20a%20placebo%20effect%2C%20but%20I%20relished%20the%20good%20feeling%20all%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneurotracker-future-of-fitness-gym-strengthens-your-brain-and-body-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712396701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f34186857f90b71522ac41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneurotracker-future-of-fitness-gym-strengthens-your-brain-and-body-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20went%20to%20a%20gym%20of%20the%20future%20in%20Singapore%2C%20where%20you%20do%20workouts%20with%20a%20NeuroTracker.%20US%20gyms%20are%20expressing%20interest%2C%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hbrueck%40businessinsider.com%20(Hilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneurotracker-future-of-fitness-gym-strengthens-your-brain-and-body-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22People%20are%20getting%20taxed%20for%20gig%20work%20they've%20never%20done%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225503%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DoorDash%20Driver%20NYC%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a818758ed31300199e0ed4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223669%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20people%20are%20getting%20tax%20forms%20suggesting%20they%20worked%20for%20apps%20like%20DoorDash%20even%20when%20they%20didn't.%3Cp%3EAlexi%20Rosenfeld%20%2F%20Contributor%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPeople%20are%20getting%20surprise%20tax%20forms%20from%20DoorDash%20and%20Uber%2C%20but%20have%20never%20worked%20there.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1099%20forms%20and%20IRS%20letters%20about%20back%20taxes%20can%20be%20signs%20someone%20used%20your%20identity%20to%20do%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-delivery-driver-gets-big-tips-declines-orders-wealthy-areas-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egig%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20delivery%20companies%20have%20been%20hacked%20recently%2C%20potentially%20giving%20details%20to%20impersonators.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20December%2C%20Brandon%20Emerson%20noticed%20a%20letter%20in%20the%20mail%20from%20the%20IRS.%20It%20claimed%20that%20his%20wife%2C%20Kelly%2C%20hadn't%20paid%20about%20%2410%2C000%20in%20taxes%20on%20income%20from%20her%20work%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-make-money-driving-for-doordash-gig-economy-rewards-program-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDoorDash%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20just%20one%20problem%3A%20Kelly%20has%20never%20worked%20for%20DoorDash%20%E2%80%94%20or%20any%20gig%20delivery%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20letter%20and%20their%20subsequent%20investigations%20showed%2C%20someone%20had%20used%20her%20Social%20Security%20number%20to%20earn%20about%20%2421%2C000%20through%20DoorDash%20over%20the%20course%20of%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20my%20wife%20didn't%20work%20for%20DoorDash%2C%26quot%3B%20Brandon%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BShe's%20been%20a%20stay-at-home%20mom%20for%20seven%20to%20eight%20years.%26quot%3B%20The%20couple%20and%20their%20children%20live%20in%20Rochester%2C%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStories%20like%20the%20Emersons'%20are%20surprisingly%20common.%20People%20who%20have%20never%20once%20delivered%20for%20a%20service%20like%20DoorDash%20suddenly%20find%20out%20that%20someone%20else%20used%20their%20name%2C%20address%2C%20Social%20Security%20number%2C%20and%20other%20details%20to%20do%20just%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20DoorDash%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20comment%20specifically%20on%20the%20Emersons'%20case%20but%20said%20that%20the%20company%20requires%20prospective%20delivery%20workers%20to%20provide%20a%20valid%20government%20ID%20and%20verifies%20multiple%20elements%20of%20their%20identity%2C%20including%20the%20Social%20Security%20number%20they%20provide%20when%20they%20sign%20up.%20The%20spokesperson%20also%20pointed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.doordash.com%2Fen-us%2Fnews%2Fan-update-on-our-work-to-build-trust-on-our-platform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20announcement%20last%20August%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20would%20re-verify%20the%20identity%20of%20its%20delivery%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20rare%20circumstances%20that%20an%20individual%20believes%20their%20identity%20was%20fraudulently%20used%20to%20dash%2C%20we%20encourage%20them%20to%20contact%20DoorDash%20support%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firs-free-tax-filing-tool-eligible-states-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIRS%20tax%20filing%20deadline%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20April%2015%20coming%20up%2C%20some%20people%20are%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20delivery%20services%20about%20taxable%20income%20they%20never%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20some%20have%20posted%20about%20Uber%20sending%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-1099%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1099%20forms%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20documentation%20of%20income%20that%20the%20companies%20have%20to%20send%20to%20independent%20contractors%20annually%20so%20that%20they%20can%20file%20their%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%