Fmediterranean-diet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebalanced%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20generally%20considered%20the%20optimal%20way%20to%20consume%20all%20the%20nutrients%20you%20need%2C%20each%20person's%20requirements%20are%20different%2C%20and%20some%20supplements%20have%20been%20shown%20to%20be%20beneficial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20six%20supplements%20Madigan%20takes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtein%20powder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%201.5%20scoops%20of%20whey%20protein%20with%20my%20breakfast%20after%20working%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Madigan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20great%20way%20to%20get%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20protein%20into%20your%20diet%20for%20not%20too%20many%20calories%2C%20and%20it%20also%20helps%20keep%20you%20full.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-protein-daily-diet-to-lose-body-fat-keep-muscle-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenough%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%20helps%20muscles%20repair%20and%20rebuild%20after%20workouts%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreatine%20monohydrate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMadigan%20said%20she%20takes%20five%20grams%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreatine-supplements-build-muscle-how-to-use-expert-advice-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreatine%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20day.%20Creatine%20is%20found%20naturally%20in%20foods%20such%20as%20red%20meat%2C%20and%20it%20helps%20the%20body%20produce%20energy%20during%20short%20bursts%20of%20intense%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreatine%20is%20well-researched%2C%20known%20to%20be%20safe%20for%20most%20adults%2C%20and%20is%20commonly%20taken%20to%20help%20people%20boost%20their%20performance%20in%20workouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlongside%20strength%20training%20and%20adequate%20nutrition%20and%20recovery%2C%20creatine%20supplementation%20can%20aid%20muscle%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlutamine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGlutamine%20is%20an%20essential%20amino%20acid%20that%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20various%20bodily%20functions.%20It's%20produced%20by%20the%20body%20and%20found%20in%20food%20such%20as%20eggs%2C%20beef%2C%20and%20tofu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPotential%20benefits%20of%20glutamine%20supplements%20include%20reducing%20muscle%20soreness%20after%20workouts%2C%20boosting%20the%20immune%20system%2C%20and%20supporting%20muscle%20recovery.%20However%2C%20studies%20suggest%20that%20it%20doesn't%20necessarily%20lead%20to%20more%20muscle%20growth%20as%20some%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHydroxymethylbutyrate%20(HMB)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20bodies%20produce%20HMB%20in%20small%20amounts%20when%20breaking%20down%20leucine%20(an%20amino%20acid%2C%20one%20of%20the%20building%20blocks%20of%20protein).%20Madigan%20said%20she%20takes%20it%20in%20the%20hope%20it%20will%20help%20her%20preserve%20lean%20muscle%20mass%2C%20enhance%20strength%20gains%2C%20and%20aid%20overall%20muscle%20function%2C%20especially%20during%20periods%20of%20increased%20physical%20stress%20or%20training%20intensity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20research%20suggests%20that%20supplementation%20can%20lead%20to%20greater%20muscle%20growth%20in%20older%20adults%20when%20combined%20with%20resistance%20training%2C%20but%20other%20studies%20have%20found%20no%20effect%2C%20and%20more%20research%20is%20needed%20to%20support%20other%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAshwagandha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMadigan%20said%20she%20takes%20ashwagandha%2C%20a%20traditional%20Ayurvedic%20medicine%2C%20to%20help%20her%20feel%20calm.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-attia-nighttime-supplements-ashwagandha-lysine-magnesium-sauna-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAshwagandha%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20herb%20that%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20reducing%20insomnia%20and%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20most%20of%20the%20studies%20on%20th