%20ton%20of%20new%20housing%20in%20recent%20years%20as%20the%20city's%20population%20has%20boomed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20its%20restrictive%20zoning%20policies%20have%20made%20affordable%2C%20medium-density%20construction%20hard%20to%20build.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20developer's%20struggles%20to%20build%20infill%20housing%20illustrate%20the%20city's%20challenges.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20Turner%20recently%20sold%20four%20homes%20that%20he%20built%20on%20what%20used%20to%20be%20a%20single%20corner%20lot%20in%20south%20central%20Austin.%20But%20the%20veteran%20real-estate%20developer%20didn't%20make%20a%20profit%20on%20the%20houses%2C%20despite%20selling%20the%20four%20of%20them%20for%20over%20%242.9%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20two%20years%20for%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20city%20departments%20to%20approve%20the%20development%2C%20which%20involved%20splitting%20one%20lot%20into%20two%2C%20and%20another%20two%20years%20for%20Turner%20to%20build%20the%20homes.%20By%20the%20time%20construction%20wrapped%20up%2C%20Austin's%20skyrocketing%20home%20prices%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kvue.com%2Farticle%2Fmoney%2Feconomy%2Fboomtown-2040%2Freports-austin-home-prices-dropping-housing-market-cooling%2F269-16959112-22ea-43af-ac3f-a1550c452877%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehad%20begun%20to%20cool%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Turner%20barely%20scraped%20by.%20%26quot%3BThe%20risk%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20too%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20do%20that%20project%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Turner's%20development%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20transformed%20one%20large%20lot%20with%20one%20house%20on%20it%20into%20two%20lots%20each%20with%20one%20larger%20home%20and%20one%20accessory%20dwelling%20unit%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0is%20exactly%20the%20kind%20of%20construction%20Austin%20and%20other%20cities%20across%20the%20country%20desperately%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurner's%20residential%20building%20company%2C%20Riverside%20Homes%2C%20specializes%20in%20infill%20development%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0small%20multifamily%20buildings%20and%20ADUs%20(also%20known%20as%20backyard%20tiny%20homes%20or%20granny%20flats).%20So-called%20%26quot%3Bmissing-middle%20housing%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20everything%20from%20an%20apartment%20to%20a%20detached%2C%20single-family%20home%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0is%20more%20affordable%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20prospective%20homeowners%20and%20renters.%20While%20Austin%20has%20been%20building%20tons%20of%20new%20apartment%20towers%2C%20it%20has%20very%20few%20townhomes%2C%20triplexes%2C%20and%20ADUs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20the%20city's%20restrictive%20zoning%20and%20land-use%20policies%20have%20made%20missing-middle%20housing%20almost%20impossible%20to%20build.%20The%20city%20heavily%20regulates%20everything%20from%20lot%20sizes%20to%20building%20heights%20to%20how%20large%20a%20home's%20footprint%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Real%20estate%20developer%20Scott%20Turner%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20the%20four%20homes%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20two%201%2C000-square-foot%20ADUs%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0that%20he%20built%20in%20south%20central%20Austin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660dcd6016bde8d4ead57650%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22850%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScott%20Turner%2C%20a%20real-estate%20developer%2C%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20the%20four%20homes%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20two%201%2C000-square-foot%20ADUs%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0he%20built%20in%20south%20central%20Austin.%3Cp%3EEliza%20Relman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Turner%2C%20subdividing%20the%20lot%20required%20a%20burdensome%20approval%20process%2C%20and%20adding%20additional%20homes%20meant%20he%20had%20to%20install%20a%20costly%20new%20utility%20pole.%20Turner%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bfor%20practical%20purposes%2C%20it%20is%20economically