S%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi's%20%26quot%3BFlop%20Film%26quot%3B%20Swipe%20At%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20At%20UP%20Rally%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20over%20the%20tie-up%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Saturday%20referred%20to%20their%20unsuccessful%20partnership%20in%202017%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20state%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bdo%20ladkon%20ki%20flop%20film%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20released%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20here%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20attacked%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20said%20while%20they%20are%20for%20%26quot%3Bcommission%26quot%3B%2C%20his%20government%20is%20on%20a%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttacking%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%20the%20party%20is%20finding%20it%20difficult%20to%20find%20candidates%20even%20from%20its%20strongholds%20and%20that%20there%20were%20instances%20where%20party%20candidates%20did%20not%20file%20nominations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20election%20I%20am%20witnessing%20where%20the%20opposition%20is%20contesting%20not%20to%20win%20but%20to%20contain%20the%20BJP%20below%20370%20seats%20and%20NDA%20400.%20Samajwadi%20Party%20is%20in%20such%20a%20condition%20that%20they%20have%20to%20change%20the%20candidates%20every%20hour%20and%20for%20Congress%2C%20it%20is%20even%20worse%2C%20they%20aren't%20finding%20candidates%2C%20even%20at%20their%20strongholds...%20'Do%20ladkon%20ki%20film%20jo%20pichali%20baar%20flop%20ho%20chuki%20hai%2C%20un%20do%20ladkon%20ki%20film%20ko%20in%20logon%20ne%20fir%20se%20release%20kiya%20hai%20(the%20film%20of%20two%20boys%2C%20which%20flopped%20last%20time%2C%20that%20these%20people%20have%20launched%20again)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20had%20held%20a%20roadshow%20in%20Agra%20in%20February%20this%20year%2C%20almost%20seven%20years%20after%20the%20Congress%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20tied%20up%20for%20the%202017%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20which%20they%20did%20not%20do%20well.%20The%20supporters%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20described%20their%20leaders%20as%20%26quot%3BUP%20ke%20ladke%26quot%3B%20during%20the%202017%20poll%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20won%20the%20trust%20of%20the%20people%20through%20its%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20is%20the%20foundation%20day%20of%20BJP.%20In%20just%20a%20few%20decades%2C%20record%20numbers%20of%20our%20countrymen%20have%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20The%20party%20has%20won%20the%20trust%20of%20the%20people%2C%20BJP%20has%20won%20the%20hearts%20of%20the%20people.%20The%20biggest%20reason%20for%20this%20is%20that%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20follow%20politics%20but%20follows%20national%20policy.%20For%20BJP%2C%20the%20nation%20comes%20first%2C%20this%20is%20not%20BJP's%20slogan%20but%20our%20article%20of%20faith%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20attacked%20the%20UPA%20rule%20saying%20that%20the%20country%20was%20going%20through%20a%20%26quot%3Bperiod%20of%20despair%20and%20crisis%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTen%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20came%20to%20Saharanpur%20for%20an%20election%20meeting.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20the%20country%20was%20going%20through%20a%20period%20of%20great%20despair%20and%20great%20crisis.%20I%20had%20guaranteed%20you%20at%20that%20time%20that%20I%20would%20not%20let%20the%20country%20bow%20down.%20I%20had%20resolved%20that%20with%20your%20blessings%2C%20I%20will%20turn%20despair%20into%20hope%2C%20hope%20into%20faith.%20You%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20your%20blessings%20and%20Modi%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20his%20hard%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20the%20BJP%20government%20works%20without%20discrimination%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20government%20also%20brought%20the%20bill%20to%20abrogate%20triple%20talaq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbrogating%20article%20370%20has%20been%20our%20mission%20and%20this%20mission%20has%20also%20been%20completed.%20The%20stones%20thrown%20by%20stone-pelters%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20Modi%20took%20that%20stone%20and%20started%20building%20Vikasit%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir...%20Today%2C%20every%20Indian%20says%2C%20'Niyat%20sahi%20to%20natije%20sahi'.%20BJP%20government%20works%20without%20any%20discrimination%2C%20we%20want%20our%20policies%20to%20reach%20everyone%20and%20for%20this%2C%20we%20have%20worked%20for%2010%20years.%20Our%20mantra%20is%20'saturation'%2C%20which%20means%20people%20should%20benefit%20100%20per%20cent%2C%20that's%20the%20real%20secularism%20and%20social%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20allegations%20of%20the%20opposition%20about%20the%20misuse%20of%20probe%20agencies%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20the%20action%20%26quot%3Bagainst%20corruption%26quot%3B%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BINDI%20alliance%20is%20for%20Commission.%20Whereas%20NDA%2C%20Modi%20government%20is%20for%20the%20mission...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaharanpur%20along%20with%20seven%20other%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20will%20go%20to%20the%20polls%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20on%20April%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712394120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fhruet3q8_pm-modi-saharanpur-ani_625x300_06_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modis-fl