%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20much%20cheaper%2C%20however%2C%20to%20move%20a%20%26quot%3Bfree%26quot%3B%20house%20onto%20a%20property%20than%20to%20construct%20an%20entirely%20new%20dwelling.%20Cohen%20said%20it%20costs%20around%20%24800%20a%20square%20foot%20to%20build%20a%20home%20on%20Nantucket%2C%20making%20that%20same%202%2C500-square-foot%20home%20cost%20about%20%242%20million%20to%20build%20from%20scratch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20live%20on%20an%20island%2C%20your%20resources%20are%20scarce%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BYou%20reuse%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHouse%20moves%20are%20so%20common%20in%20Nantucket%20they%20hold%20up%20traffic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnantucketcurrent.com%2Fnews%2Fnantucket-has-the-most-house-moves-in-the-state-is-that-too-many%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHouse%20moves%20in%20Nantucket%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20increased%20in%20popularity.%20A%20decade%20ago%2C%20Nantucket%20only%20issued%2019%20permits%20for%20homes%20or%20units%20to%20be%20transported%20across%20the%20island%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Nantucket%20Current.%20In%202022%2C%2091%20permits%20were%20issued%20by%20October%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20and%20many%20house%20moves%20happen%20in%20the%20off-season%20months%20late%20in%20the%20year%2C%20so%20the%20annual%20figure%20was%20likely%20even%20higher%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Current.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2sZw5MvW4b%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2sZw5MvW4b%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C