%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20get%20to%20work%20late%20and%20you%20tell%20your%20boss%2C%20'Oh%2C%20there's%20a%20house%20move%2C'%20people%20just%20understand%2C%26quot%3B%20Kuszpa%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20of%20the%20'free'%20homes%20do%20good%20for%20the%20community%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Straight%20Wharf%2C%20Nantucket%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e4a862bd98a600197bb682%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20of%20Nantucket's%20year-round%20workforce%20lives%20in%20repurposed%20%26quot%3Bfree%26quot%3B%20homes.%20%3Cp%3EMaremagnum%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBuyers%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bfree%26quot%3B%20homes%20fall%20into%20three%20main%20categories%2C%20Cohen%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20group%20is%20homeowners%20on%20Nantucket%20looking%20for%20a%20small%20property%20to%20turn%20into%20a%20rental%20for%20additional%20income.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20pool%2C%20which%20Cohen%20said%20is%20larger%2C%20consists%20of%20individuals%20or%20young%20families%20who%2C%20through%20their%20families%20or%20other%20connections%2C%20already%20have%20land%20on%20the%20island%20but%20not%20enough%20wealth%20for%20a%20new-construction%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20category%20is%20housing%20nonprofits%20that%20take%20the%20homes%20as%20a%20donation%20%E2%80%94%20giving%20a%20tax%20break%20to%20the%20sellers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20turn%20the%20structures%20into%20affordable%20housing%20for%20the%20local%20workforce%20and%20low-income%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20cheapest%20way%20to%20create%20housing%2C%26quot%3B%20Kuszpa%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20homes%20are%20only%20open%20to%20families%20making%20less%20than%20110%25%20of%20the%20area's%20median%20inco