n%20between%20the%20couple.%20The%20High%20Court%20cited%20the%20trial%20court's%20finding%2C%20which%20concluded%20that%20the%20man%20and%20woman%20had%20been%20living%20as%20husband%20and%20wife.%20Additionally%2C%20considering%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20child%20within%20the%20relationship%2C%20the%20court%20affirmed%20the%20woman's%20entitlement%20to%20maintenance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20landmark%20decision%20underscores%20the%20evolving%20legal%20landscape%20regarding%20live-in%20relationships%20in%20India.%20It%20signifies%20a%20departure%20from%20traditional%20norms%20and%20a%20recognition%20of%20the%20rights%20and%20vulnerabilities%20of%20women%20in%20such%20partnerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Uttarakhand%20brought%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%20to%20provide%20a%20legal%20framework%20for%20uniform%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20land%2C%20property%2C%20and%20inheritance%20laws%20for%20all%20citizens.%20One%20of%20the%20sections%20of%20the%20bill%20made%20registration%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20mandatory.%20It%20also%20states%20that%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20couple%20will%20be%20notified%20if%20they%20are%20adults%20under%20the%20age%20of%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712390340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fgdieuj5k_couple-generic_625x300_06_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-courts-unique-order-on-breakup-after-a-live-in-relationship-5386379%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20has%20taken%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20recognizing%20the%20rights%20of%20women%20in%20live-in%20relationships%20by%20ruling%20that%20a%20woman%20living%20with%20a%20man%20for%20a%20considerable%20period%20is%20entitled%20to%20maintenance%20upon%20separation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-courts-unique-order-on-breakup-aft