le%20Geeta%20was%20a%20homemaker%20for%20most%20of%20her%20life%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20convert%20this%20challenge%20into%20an%20opportunity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%202016%20to%202020%2C%20the%20business%20was%20run%20from%20the%20home%20kitchen%2C%20without%20any%20formal%20branding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20with%20her%20son%20Vinit%2C%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286270%2Fmom-sells-authentic-maharashtrian-food-in-mumbai-pune-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformally%20launched%20Patil%20Kaki%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94-%20a%20brand%20that%20sells%20%3Cem%3Emodak%2C%20puranpoli%2C%20chakli%2C%20poha%2C%20chivda%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20much%20more.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20interview%2C%20she%20had%20over%203000%20customers%20and%20earned%20Rs%201%20crore%20annually%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20interview%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Tapping%20the%20right%20food%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20Krishna%20Popuri%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Health%20Sutra%2C%20a%20millet-based%20startup%2C%20was%20always%20interested%20in%20starting%20a%20food%20business.%20However%2C%20he%20lacked%20direction.%20After%20completing%20his%20engineering%20from%20IIT-Delhi%2C%20he%20started%20to%20work%20a%20corporate%20job%20while%20looking%20for%20ideas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20this%20time%20that%20his%20father%20developed%20diabetes%20and%20was%20advised%20to%20consume%20millet.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20know%20more%20about%20them%2C%20I%20spoke%20to%20an%20aunt%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20food%20science%20department%20at%20a%20university%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20She%20was%20the%20one%20who%20told%20me%20how%20they%20are%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20next%20big%20thing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20with%20his%20gut%20and%20his%20aunt%E2%80%99s%20advice%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338546%2Fmillet-startup-revenue-in-crores-ready-to-eat-food-health-sutra-hyderabad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20started%20Health%20Sutra%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20true%20enough%2C%20even%20the%20Indian%20government%20designated%20it%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CYear%20of%20Millets%E2%80%9D.%20The%20company%20sells%20cereal%20flakes%20such%20as%20Jowar%20Flakes%2C%20Ragi%20Flakes%2C%20and%20Barley%20Flakes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20seven%20different%20types%20of%20%3Cem%3Erava%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Eupma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20biscuits%20made%20from%20ragi%20and%20jowar.%20The%20brand%20has%20clocked%20an%20impressive%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%202.5%20crores%20since%20its%20inception.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sai%20created%20Health%20Sutra%20to%20bring%20millet%20alternatives%20to%20the%20market.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Health%20Sutra.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338561%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESai%20created%20Health%20Sutra%20to%20bring%20mil