mata%20Banerjee's%20Counter%20After%20Anti-Terror%20Agency%20Team%20Attacked%20In%20Bengal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAnti-terror%20agency%20NIA%20today%20arrested%20two%20key%20conspirators%20in%20connection%20with%20the%202022%20Bhupatinagar%20bomb%20blast%20case%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20East%20Midnapore%20district.%20However%2C%20the%20team%20sent%20to%20Bhupatinagar%20was%20attacked%20during%20the%20raids%20this%20morning%2C%20with%20one%20NIA%20official%20injured.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrested%20individuals%2C%20Balai%20Charan%20Maity%20and%20Manobrata%20Jana%2C%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20following%20extensive%20searches%20conducted%20at%20five%20different%20locations%2C%20including%20Jana's%20residence.%C2%A0As%20the%20team%20commenced%20its%20search%20operation%2C%20they%20were%20suddenly%20confronted%20by%20a%20hostile%20mob.%20The%20situation%20quickly%20escalated%20as%20the%20mob%20launched%20an%20assault%20on%20the%20NIA%20officers%2C%20resulting%20in%20damage%20to%20property%2C%20including%20the%20breaking%20of%20a%20vehicle's%20windscreen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aggressive%20resistance%20was%20aimed%20at%20halting%20the%20NIA%20team%20and%20stopping%20the%20officials%20from%20reaching%20the%20Bhupatinagar%20police%20station%20for%20the%20completion%20of%20arrest%20formalities.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20NIA%20has%20filed%20a%20complaint%20at%20the%20local%20police%20station%20regarding%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NIA%2C%20Manobrata%20Jana%20and%20Balai%20Charan%20Maity%20were%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20manufacture%20and%20detonate%20crude%20bombs.%20The%20December%202022%20explosion%2C%20which%20killed%20three%20people%2C%20took%20place%20in%20the%20house%20of%20Rajkumar%20Manna%20in%20Naruabilla%20village%20of%20East%20Medinipur%20district.%20Rajkumar%20Manna%2C%20along%20with%20Biswajit%20Gayen%20and%20Buddhadeb%20Manna%2C%20died%20in%20the%20blast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Police%20registered%20a%20an%20FIR%20on%20December%203%2C%202022.%20However%2C%20the%20Explosive%20Substances%20Act%20was%20not%20initially%20applied%20in%20the%20case.%20Subsequently%2C%20a%20writ%20petition%20was%20filed%20at%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%2C%20urging%20the%20inclusion%20of%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20Act%20and%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20case%20to%20the%20NIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20large%20police%20contingent%20was%20dispatched%20to%20the%20scene%20to%20bring%20the%20situation%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20president%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20alleged%20that%20the%20NIA%20was%20working%20for%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20did%20they%20raid%20at%20midnight%3F%20Did%20they%20have%20police%20permission%3F%20Locals%20reacted%20in%20the%20way%20they%20would%20have%20if%20any%20other%20stranger%20had%20visited%20the%20place%20at%20midnight.%20Why%20are%20they%20arresting%20people%20right%20before%20the%20elections%3F%20What%20does%20the%20BJP%20think%2C%20that%20they%20will%20arrest%20every%20booth%20agent%3F%20What%20right%20does%20NIA%20have%3F%20They%20are%20doing%20all%20these%20to%20support%20the%20BJP.%20We%20call%20upon%20the%20entire%20world%20to%20fight%20against%20this%20BJP's%20dirty%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20accused%20NIA%20personnel%20of%20assaulting%20residents%20in%20Bhupatinagar%20rather%20than%20the%20villagers%20initiating%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20the%20women%20sit%20back%20if%20they%20are%20attacked%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%20chief%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20trying%20to%20use%20the%20central%20agencies%20to%20win%20the%20elections.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20work%20impartially%2C%20not%20turn%20into%20a%20BJP-run%20commission%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712381100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fk1u84rso_nia-team-attacked-in-east-midnapore-_625x300_06_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanti-terror-agency-officials-attacked-their-vehicle-vandalised-in-west-bengals-east-midnapore-district-5385613%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20team%20of%20the%20anti-terror%20agency%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20was%20attacked%20during%20a%20raid%20in%20Bengal's%20East%20Midnapore%20district%20this%20morning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanti-terror-agency-officials-attacked-their-vehicle-vandalised-in-west-bengals-east-midnapore-district-5385613%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanti-terror-agency-officials-attacked-their-vehicle-vandalised-in-west-bengals-east-midnapore-district-5385613%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanti-terror-agency-officials-attacked-their-vehicle-vandalised-in-west-bengals-east-midnapore-district-5385613%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20pushes%20back%20on%20US%20treasury%20secretary%20Yellen's%20excess%20capacity%20stance%20as%20meetings%20run%20long%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712381080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109081334%2Cimgsize-37390.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-pushes-back-on-us-treasury-secretary-yellens-excess-capacity-stance-as-meetings-run-long%2Farticleshow%2F109081291.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109081291.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EChina%