mavar-Boson-Whitewater-1712316714-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346666%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVikas%20Brahmavar%2C%20founder%20of%20Boson%20Whitewater%2C%20spoke%20to%20The%20Better%20India%20about%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20water%20scarcity%20problem%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20any%20city%20in%20India%2C%20when%20authorities%20plan%20water%20distribution%2C%20they%20never%20look%20at%20what%20is%20going%20out%20of%20the%20city.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20developed%20cities%20like%20Singapore%2C%20the%20planning%20is%20not%20based%20on%20freshwater%20available%20in%20dams%20but%20based%20on%20the%20predictable%20wastewater%20which%20is%20going%20out%20of%20the%20city%2C%20because%20that%20can%20be%20estimated%20clearly%20based%20on%20the%20population%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vikas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20population%20of%20a%20given%20city%20is%20known%2C%20authorities%20in%20places%20like%20Singapore%20know%20exactly%20the%20amount%20of%20wastewater%20which%20is%20going%20out.%20From%20the%20volume%20wastewater%20estimated%2C%20authorities%20can%20then%20gauge%20which%20industries%20can%20be%20covered%20by%20that%20treated%20wastewater%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20policy%2C%20their%20starting%20point%20is%20wastewater%2C%20which%20addresses%20sanitation%20as%20well%20as%20industrial%20water%20requirements%2C%20and%20then%20they%20look%20at%20the%20freshwater%20available%20from%20dams%20or%20other%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20big%20mindset%20change%20has%20to%20come.%20Any%20developing%20country%20should%20have%20this%20mindset%20of%20looking%20at%20wastewater%20first%20before%20looking%20at%20freshwater%20options%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Vikas.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Boson%20Whitewater%