ly%20discoverable%20places.%20And%20the%20credit%20goes%20to%20the%20vibrant%20palette%20that%20boasts%20striking%20pastels%20and%20modern%20finishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dairy%E2%80%99s%20metamorphosis%20from%20the%20old%20factory%20look%20to%20the%20now%20spruced-up%20interiors%20made%20waves%20in%20September%20last%20year.%20But%20as%20Sarfaraz%20Irani%20(39)%20who%20heads%20the%20sales%20department%20shares%2C%20the%20family%20has%20always%20loved%20experimenting.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20once%20when%20we%20were%20kids%2C%20we%20had%20all%20our%20family%20members%20over%20to%20help%20us%20paint%20one%20of%20the%20storerooms.%20We%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20vibrant.%20As%20a%20family%2C%20we%20all%20got%20together%20with%20paintbrushes%20and%20got%20the%20whole%20place%20to%20look%20amazing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20the%20activity%20was%20a%20success%20then%2C%20just%20like%20the%20revamped%20interiors%20are%20now.%20While%20some%20of%20the%20siblings%20cherish%20these%20family%20activities%2C%20the%20others%20hold%20fond%20memories%20involving%20the%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParvana%20Mistry%20(36)%20who%20now%20heads%20operations%20at%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%20recalls%20hours%20spent%20at%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekarkhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20(factory)%20when%20she%20was%20little.%20Her%20ears%20would%20perk%20up%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340041%2Fentrepreneur-save-family-business-harshit-tanay-agrawal-pistabarfi-cloud-kitchen-janta-dairy-sweets-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esizzle%20of%20the%20sweets%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20prepared%20and%20her%20eyes%20would%20longingly%20watch%20the%20fresh%20piles%20of%20%3Cem%3Esutarfeni%20%3C%2Fem%3E(an%20Indian%20speciality%20made%20with%20flour%20roasted%20in%20ghee%20and%20blended%20with%20melted%20sugar)%2C%20eagerly%20awaiting%20her%20turn%20to%20taste.%3C%2F