having%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337104%2Feasy-recipe-for-gajar-ka-halwa-history-winter-dessert%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20legacy%20%3C%2Fa%3Elike%20this%2C%20says%20Parvana%2C%20is%20that%20most%20of%20the%20sweets%20are%20older%20than%20her.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20mind%20you%2C%20they%20are%20still%20made%20with%20the%20same%20recipe%20as%20they%20were.%20We%20make%20our%20sweets%20with%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20delight%2C%20precision%2C%20and%20tradition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-4-1711120511.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20the%20years%20the%20dairy%20has%20seen%20guests%20the%20likes%20of%20Mumtaz%2C%20Jim%20Sarbh%2C%20Boman%20Irani%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-4-1711120511.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-4-1711120511-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-4-1711120511-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-4-1711120511-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-4-1711120511-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345658%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThrough%20the%20years%20the%20dairy%20has%20seen%20guests%20the%20likes%20of%20Mumtaz%2C%20Jim%20Sarbh%2C%20Boman%20Irani%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Zeenia%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigu