0adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F62683%2Fabortion-laws-india-supreme-court-rape-survivor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterminating%20pregnancies%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebeyond%2020%20weeks%20a%20criminal%20offence%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20gone%20through%20the%20MTP%20Act%20multiple%20times%20and%20thoroughly%20researched%20the%20topic%20only%20to%20find%20out%20that%20the%20set%20limit%20was%20arbitrary.%20There%20was%20no%20reason%20to%20support%20why%20it%20was%20set%20to%2020%20weeks%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Nikhil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20if%20a%20woman%20is%2019%20weeks%20pregnant%2C%20then%20doctors%20will%20not%20even%20blink%20before%20terminating%20the%20pregnancy%20but%20when%20she%20is%20at%2021%20weeks%2C%20that%20becomes%20a%20problem.%20The%20termination%20of%20pregnancy%20is%20primarily%20meant%20for%20major%20and%20substantial%20abnormalities.%20You%20are%20refusing%20it%20because%20she%20has%20crossed%20over%20some%20arbitrary%20limit.%20As%20a%20specialist%2C%20I%20know%20that%20it%20is%20safe%20to%20terminate%20the%20pregnancy%20beyond%2020%20weeks.%20We%20are%20not%20in%201971%20anymore!%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-1-1711970332.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Nikhil%20opined%20it%20was%20unfair%20to%20punish%20women%20by%20forcing%20them%20to%20give%20birth%20to%20intellectually%20or%20physically%20disabled%20infants.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-1-1711970332.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-1-1711