E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20their%20plea%20was%20rejected.%20But%20this%20did%20not%20deter%20his%20resolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%2014-year-long%20fight%20for%20abortion%20rights%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%20in%202016%2C%20Dr%20Nikhil%20was%20put%20in%20a%20similar%20situation.%20%E2%80%9CA%20minor%20rape%20survivor%20was%20brought%20to%20me%20by%20a%20non-profit%20organisation.%20She%20was%2024%20weeks%20pregnant%20and%20the%20foetus%E2%80%99%20brain%20was%20not%20developed.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20the%20foetus%20stays%20alive%20till%20the%20umbilical%20cord%20is%20intact.%20As%20soon%20as%20the%20cord%20is%20clamped%20and%20cut%2C%20it%20dies.%20Given%20the%20sensitivity%2C%20nobody%20wanted%20to%20touch%20this%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20justice%20for%20these%20women.%20He%20got%20his%20first%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20apex%20court%20when%20he%20garnered%20the%20support%20of%20320%20women%20who%20had%20abnormal%20foetuses%2C%20were%20minor%20rape%20survivors%20and%20from%20low%20socio-economic%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202019%2C%20Dr%20Nikhil%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20justice%20for%20women.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fu