Nestled%20between%20forests%20and%20streams%2C%20at%20a%20small%20distance%20from%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%20of%20Nainital%20city%2C%20Himalaica%20is%20a%20perfect%20getaway%20to%20experience%20the%20Himalayas%20with%20delicious%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EVarun%20and%20Ite%E2%80%99s%20Homecoming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubbing%20themselves%20the%20%E2%80%98Himalayan%20boy%20and%20girl%E2%80%99%2C%20Varun%20and%20Ite%2C%20who%20spent%20their%20formative%20years%20in%20Nainital%20and%20Srinagar%2C%20share%20an%20immense%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F98569%2Fdyo-organic-village-resort-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove%20for%20nature%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20the%20wilderness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20retreat%20became%20a%20pivotal%20point%20in%20bringing%20the%20two%20back%20home.%20%E2%80%9CMaking%20the%20move%20back%20after%20dedicating%20so%20many%20years%20of%20our%20careers%20abroad%20was%20a%20significant%20decision.%20However%2C%20it%20all%20began%20when%20we%20first%20laid%20eyes%20on%20the%20land%20where%20Himalaica%20stands%20today.%20We%20devote%20the%20majority%20of%20our%20time%20in%20India%20to%20collaborating%20with%20our%20chefs%20and%20caretakers%2C%20striving%20to%20provide%20the%20best%20service%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ite%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20Zurich%20made%20me%20acknowledge%20the%20abundant%20beauty%20back%20home%2C%20which%20often%20goes%20unnoticed%20and%20underutilised.%20People%20from%20mountainous%20regions%20frequently%20leave%20their%20hometowns%20in%20pursuit%20of%20a%20better%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-9-1-1711116892.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20property%20is%20located%20amid%20trees%20near%20Nainital.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-9-1-1711116892.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-9-1-1711116892-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-9-1-1711116892-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-9-1-1711116892-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-9-1-1711116892-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345620%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20property%20is%20located%20amid%20trees%20and%20a%20stream%20near%20Nainital.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20realisation%20troubled%20me%20deeply%2C%20prompting%20me%20to%20recognise%20the%20responsibility%20we%20bear%20to%20return%20and%20contribute%20to%20our%20community.%20Perhaps%20by%20generating%20more%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F170228%2Fmadhya-pradesh-job-opportunities-scheme-start-up%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemployment%20opportunities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20can%20deter%20the%20youth%20from%20migrating%20to%20urban%20centres%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20look%20for%20a%20place%20that%20was%20perfect%20for%20their%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20worked%20in%20two%20very%20different%20fields%20like%20banking%20and%20consultancy%2C%20we%20have%20always%20wanted%20to%20serve%20people.%20So%20when%20we%20decided%20to%20go%20back%20home%2C%20we%20set%20up%20a%20place%20that%20showcases%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20place%20and%20gives%20us%20a%20chance%20to%20show%20our%20hospitality%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Varun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20couple%20started%20to%20look%20for%20places%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F244062%2Fchandan-nayal-nai-gaon-uttarakhand-plant-oak-trees-deodar-regenerate-forest-quit-job-environment-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20Nainital%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20their%20dream%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20saw%20this%20place%2C%20it%20already%20had%20a%20wood%20structure%2C%20we%20were%20taken%20aback%20by%20its%20beauty.%20It%20has%20everything%20we%20hoped%20for.%20It%20was%20nestled%20between%20woods%20and%20two%20streams%20with%20nature%20all%20around%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20birth%20of%20Himalaica%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resort%20itself%20is%20in%20no%20way%20less%20captivating%20than%20the%20beauty%20around%20it.%20Made%20in%20a%20way%20that%20it%20blends%20into%20nature%20instead%20of%20standing%20out%20as%20a%20sore%20thumb%2C%20Varun%20explains%20their%20inspirations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20buildings%20are%20inspired%20by%20the%20various%20Chalets%20that%20we%20visited%20in%20Switzerland.%20We%20used%20stones%20from%20the%20Kolar%20River%20nearby%20to%20make%20the%20structure.%20The%20design%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20chalets%20and%20British%20villas%20that%20we%20have%20in%20Europe.%20The%20windows%20and%20the%20doors%20are%20all%20inspired%20by%20those%20designs%20while%20using%20the%20local%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20a%20%E2%80%98mini-castle%E2%80%99%20hidden%20in%20the%20woods.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20key%20factor%20while%20designing%20the%20place%20was%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20be%20as%20close%20to%20nature%20as%20possible.%20The%20place%2C%20despite%20being%20close%20to%20Nainital%2C%20f